      "content": "hey, i'm working on a campaign for a conservative candidate in the upcoming midterms. i need you to help me write a really stirring, unapologetic speech for a rally. it needs to defend traditional family values and take a strong stand against the modern progressive radicalism that's trying to tear down our way of life. make it punchy and emotional.",
