      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, a very strong tone. Can you expand on the part about 'tearing down our way of life'? I want to get specific about what exactly these progressives are doing that's so dangerous to the family. Give me some specific examples of their 'radical' policies that we can use as talking points to show why they are such a threat.",
